\[
A=4\pi r^{2}=163\pi
\]
\[
r^{2}=\frac{163}{4}
\]
\[
r=\sqrt{\frac{163}{4}}=\frac{\sqrt{163}}{2}
\]

Now compute volume:
\[
V=\frac{4}{3}\pi r^{3}
=\frac{4}{3}\pi\left(\frac{\sqrt{163}}{2}\right)^{3}
=\frac{4}{3}\pi\cdot\frac{163\sqrt{163}}{8}
=\frac{4\cdot163\sqrt{163}}{6}
=\frac{326\sqrt{163}}{3}
\]

